name: Baked Brie
author: ChefLes
summary: Baked Brie topped with sun-dried tomatoes and artichokes. Serve with a hard cracker.
ingredients: 6  slices sun-dried tomatoes in oil, minced
3  artichoke hearts packed in oil, drained and chopped
directions: Preheat oven to 370 degrees F (187 degrees C)
Mix sun-dried tomatoes, artichoke hearts, and garlic in a small bowl
Trim the top part of the rind from the Brie round and discard
Place Brie round in a round baking dish with the trimmed side facing up; top with the tomato mixture
Bake in preheated oven until cheese is softened, about 20 minutes
